<h2>Burn baby</h2>
<p>Under Petrini, a new pharmacy was added to the Juliusspital, but it burned down. After that it was rebuilt in Baroque style.</p>

<h2>garden</h2>
<p>Prince-bishop Guttenberg had built a botanical garden and Greising later added a pavilion.</p>

<h2>Well</h2>
<p>The Baroque well uses a special Baroque technique. Four water streams flow into the well as an allegory of the four Franconian rivers: the Main, Tauber, Sinn and Saale.</p>